    <a href="#about">About</a>
  </nav>

<div class="intro">
    <div class="intro-left">
      <p class="tagline">
        Creative Designer &amp; Developer specializing in Visual &amp; Web Design, and
        Front-End.
      </p>
      <p class="status">
        Open to work — <a class="email" href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="intro-right">
      <p>
        An open index of my web builds, UI concepts, and editorial layouts. This is a space
        for all the work — from raw concepts to finished work.
      </p>
      <p>
        Just breaking grids, testing typefaces, building concepts, and experimenting out in
        the open.
      </p>
      <p class="divider">( Selected and Unselected )</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</header>